column5: Just book trip to Witch Bay Camp. July 15-19 Can't wait!

LOVE it. Steve and Gail (the owners) are the best!!! Great fishing, great accommodations, great food, great people who fish there (some PWT pros too!!!). When are you going? We, brother and I, will be going mid-Summer next year also.
LOL I'm going to guess somewhere around July.........15 to the 19th?????
